                    <i class="fa fa-music"></i> Music Bot
                </h3>
                <p>
                    Get exclusive <em>early access</em> to the Discord and Skype music bot!
                    Other features include:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Cross platform music syncing</li>
                    <li>Queue whole YouTube playlists</li>
                    <li>Play songs longer than 10 minutes</li>
                    <li>Web panel access</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-one-third">
            <div class="content">
                <h3 style="text-align: center">
                    <i class="fa fa-star-o"></i> Early access to new features
                </h3>
                <p>
                    If you purchase a premium plan for GenieBot,
                    you get early access to new features before
                    anybody else! A few planned features:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Minecraft server plugin support</li>
                    <li>Build your own chat AI</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <br />
    <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-one-third">
            <div class="content">
                <h3 style="text-align: center">
                    <i class="fa fa-users"></i> Language translations
                </h3>
                <p>
                    Premium users can use language translations, with up to
                    50 sentence translations per day! Powered by Google Translate.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-one-third">
            <div class="content">
                <h3 style="text-align: center">
                    <i class="fa fa-shield"></i> Advanced chat moderation
                </h3>
                <p>
                    Moderation tools for premium users are faster and more advanced.
                    Here's what puts it aside from free users:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Machine learning spam protection</li>
                    <li>Warning configurations system</li>
                    <li>Public moderation log webpage</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-one-third">
            <div class="content">
                <h3 style="text-align: center">
                    <i class="fa fa-desktop"></i> More website screenshots
                </h3>
                <p>
                    GenieBot premium users can take up to 25 daily website screenshots
                    whereas free users are able to take 3 per day.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="columns">
    <div class="column is-one-third">
        <div class="box">
            <div class="box-head" style="text-align: center">
                <p style="font-size: 65px">
                    <strong>$5</strong>
